    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Seat Tracks</title>
        <para>Seat tracks (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700376">Figure 76, Item 3</hotlnk>) are available for various seat configurations and seat
            type applications. Seat tracks and wheelchair tie downs are available for different configurations of
            seating plans when required. The tracks are mounted to the floor and use a stud and locking clip (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700376">Figure 76, Items 1 and 2</hotlnk>) to allow the movement of seat rows as required.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700376" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700376.webp" filename="../figg47/G4700376.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 76. Seat Track and Seat Mounting Studs</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT MOUNTING STUD</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT STUD RETAINER CLIP</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT TRACK</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>Seat tracks may be installed to facilitate various width seat rows.</para>
        <figure id="f4700377" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700377.webp" filename="../figg47/G4700377.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 77. Seat Track and Seat Mounting Base</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT ASSEMBLY LEGS</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT MOUNTING STUDS AND NUTS</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT TRACK</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">RIBBED AISLE FLOORING</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SEAT MOUNTING BASE</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>
            <title>Wheel Chair Shoulder Harness Mounting and Storage</title>
        </para>
        <para>Shoulder harness tracks (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700378">Figure 78, Item 2</hotlnk>) are an available option used in conjunction with
            wheelchair floor track. The seat belt and harness assembly are stored in a secured carrying bag (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700379">Figure 79, Item 2</hotlnk>) attached to the shoulder harness track assembly.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700378" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700378.webp" filename="../figg47/G4700378.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="288px"/>
            <caption>Figure 78. Shoulder Harness Track</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SHOULDER HARNESS ATTACHMENT ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SHOULDER HARNESS TRACK</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SHOULDER HARNESS TRACK MOUNTING BOLTS</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SHOULDER HARNESS BELT</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f4700379" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700379.webp" filename="../figg47/G4700379.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 79. Shoulder Harness Storage Bag</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">HARNESS BAG MOUNTING SCREWS</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">SHOULDER HARNESS STORAGE BAG</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
